title: 1.14纯净服崩溃报错
author: Alrolg
txt_content:
1.14.4的spigot
玩了很久后 突然出现这个 
然后服务端就崩溃了
再次启动，只要玩家一进入 
就会继续奔溃 
第一次遇到这种..

replies.txt_content:
本帖最后由 a1294790523 于 2019-11-21 09:44 编辑 
Alrolg 发表于 2019-11-21 09:13
今天的报错日志[09:10:09] [Server thread/INFO]: [CitizensBooks] An update for CitizensBooks (v2.5.3) is available!
[09:10:09] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 2/INFO]: [Vault] There was an issue attempting to check for the latest version.
[09:10:09] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 2/INFO]: [Vault] No new version available
[09:10:10] [Server thread/INFO]: [0;32;22m[QuantumShop/INFO] [0;37;22mAuto-save: Saved [0;37;1m0 online users [0;37;22m| [0;37;1m0 offline users[0;37;22m.[m
[09:10:10] [Server thread/INFO]: Starting UUID caching[m
[09:10:10] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 3/INFO]: [PlaceholderAPI] 163 placeholder expansions are available on the cloud.
[09:10:10] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 18/INFO]: [0;30;1m[[0;33;22m地皮系统[0;30;1m] [0;37;22mStarting player data caching for: world[m
[09:10:10] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 18/INFO]: [0;30;1m[[0;33;22m地皮系统[0;30;1m] [0;37;22m[0;33;22mCached a total of: 7 UUIDs[m
[09:10:10] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 2/INFO]: [Images] Loaded 3 images...
[09:10:10] [Server thread/INFO]: [CitizensBooks] Succesfully downloaded update!
[09:10:10] [Server thread/INFO]: [CitizensBooks] Shuting down the server!
[09:10:10] [Server thread/INFO]: Stopping server你一开始的报错是正常的，正常来说插件不会考虑服务器一启动就关闭的特殊情况
所以就这样了

解决方法二选一:
1.禁用CitizensBooks插件的自动更新
2.更新CitizensBooks插件
